actor Customer
participant KIOSK
participant SPP
participant MADAPI
participant CLM
participant NIMC

opt National or Foreigner with NIN
Customer->KIOSK : Enters NIN detail
KIOSK->SPP: Validate NIN details
SPP->CLM: Perform NIN eligibility check
CLM->SPP: Returns the eligibility check response
SPP->MADAPI: Validate and fetch NIN Details \n(including Biodata and Image)
MADAPI->NIMC: sends NIN validation call
NIMC->MADAPI: Returns NIN details
MADAPI->SPP: Returns NIN details
SPP->SPP:   Perform NIN  \n underage Check
SPP->KIOSK: Returns NIN Details
KIOSK->KIOSK: Temporarily keep NIN \n Data in memory
end
opt Foreigner without NIN
KIOSK->Customer: Prompt to enter passport details
Customer->KIOSK: Fill in Passport Details
end
KIOSK->KIOSK: Transition to Biometric Capture\n screen
